I've been a web designer since 1998, providing hand-coded website design, online marketing, social media, and search engine optimization (SEO) services. My focus is on small business web design.

I've been doing web design and small business marketing for over two decades, this is my full-time business (not something I do "on the side"), and I am located in the U.S. (Southern New Jersey).

You will work directly with me (Teri Brooks), not a member of a corporation that treats you like a number. And I do ALL the work myself... NO outsourcing!
You will own your website, and your domain name will be under YOUR name, not mine.

I won't lock you into an annual contract for your website, and I don't charge monthly fees for your website unless you choose to pay that way.

I don't cut corners. I'll manually "hand-code" your website from scratch instead of using template websites like WordPress, as most web designers do. Hand-coded websites are more search friendly, more customizable, and less vulnerable to security issues.

I won't "drop the ball", and I'll answer the phone or call you back right away. And because I know you have a hectic schedule, I will contact you to get information to complete your website, rather than you having to remind me.

company_description:
2 Green Chicks provides green cleaning, organizing, and intelligent packing services. We are locally owned and operated and blend an appreciation for cleanliness with a commitment to a greener lifestyle. We don't think you should have to sacrifice precious free time with your loved ones to have a beautiful home.

Our goal is to create healthier homes using eco-friendly practices. 2 Green Chicks provides Green Cleaning using natural, biodegradable, and nontoxic cleaning supplies. Green cleaning is good for allergy and asthma sufferers and anyone chemically sensitive who have heightened concerns for what cleaners are used in their home. We provide a high level of service at a reasonable price. Our ultimate goal is to welcome you home to a clean space that is at once relaxing, rejuvenating, and stimulating to the senses.

A majority of cleaning companies have on the job training. Cleaning can be complicated and our teams are extensively trained (on our own homes) before they enter your home. We aren't a large chain so you won't see a revolving door of employees coming to your home to clean. You will begin to build a healthy and trusting relationship with our owners and employees as we strive to send the same crew to your home to clean each time. 

Our other services include home and office organizing - whether you need a new filing system or an entire house organized, let us efficiently change your space into a pleasant, organized area.
